---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — TRT Clinic Finder">
  <section class="container-prose pt-20 pb-24 max-w-2xl prose prose-ink">
    <h1 class="font-display">About</h1>
    <p>
      TRT Clinic Finder is an independent directory of testosterone and hormone replacement therapy clinics across the United States. Every listing is cataloged from public sources — nobody buys placement, and nobody gets removed for not paying.
    </p>
    <p>
      The directory exists so the guy who needs TRT can see every real option in his city, not just the three clinics with the biggest ad budgets.
    </p>
    <h2>How we catalog clinics</h2>
    <p>
      We pull clinic data from Google Places using searches for TRT, HRT, and hormone-optimization keywords per metro area, then deduplicate and tag services based on what the clinic publishes publicly. Data is refreshed periodically.
    </p>
    <h2>This is not medical advice</h2>
    <p>
      Information on this site is educational only. Talk to a licensed clinician before starting, changing, or stopping any hormone therapy.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
